data.description: **ASK YOUR AGENT TODAY ABOUT SELLERS OFFER TO BUYER** Here's your chance to live in Sanford’s most prestigious and historical Rosemount-McIver park. The William L. Jewell House was built in 1927 by Mr. Jewell himself. The home provides 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Many historical features still in tact with several modern updates. Sit in the living room this fall reading a book with all your french doors open to enjoy the cool breeze, host Thanksgiving dinner in your formal dining room, or enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage just outside the primary suite on your balcony. It's hard to find a home like this anymore, so get there to see it today! **ASK YOUR AGENT TODAY ABOUT SELLERS OFFER TO BUYER**
